      <div id="infopanelrow2">
        "Hi, welcome to another programmer's portfolio. I'm a programmer, and yes that's it.
        I love to code. Now, this's a statement right here in itself. My main domain in IT is related to Machine Learning and
        my dream is to one day use this technology at such a large scale for the betterment of people that life without it becomes simply
        unimaginable. Yes, my biggest vision for myself is to help the society enjoy their lives to the fullest in the easiest possible manner. My other ambition
        is to support as many freelancers and people with talent in CSE with a platform which allows them to showcase their skills at no or extremely low
        costs. Apart from ML, I do full stack web development using PHP for backend, desktop application development using Java Swing and Android application development as a hobby
        in IT, and my 'non-IT' passions include speedcubing and reading. I'm a fan of music and maths and that's probably... all of me (quite literally)."
      </div>
